text: Yulia, Julia, or Yuliya Ivanova may refer to: * Yuliya Ivanova (cross-country skier) (born 1985), Russian cross-country skier * Yulia Ivanova (model) (born 1983), Russian beauty queen and model * Yuliya Ivanova (rhythmic gymnast) (born 1977), Russian rhythmic gymnast * Yuliya Zaripova (born 1986), née Ivanova, Russian middle-distance runner
title: Yulia Ivanova
